data.description: This beautiful 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home is located in the AMAZING Avalon Park. Inside the community is everything you'll ever need, Shopping Centers, Gas Stations, Banks, Restaurants, and MUCH MORE!!! The community itself is close and convenient to all emenities, Entertainment, UCF, 408, 417 and more!! This beautiful home features a spacious floor plan with an island counter in kitchen and a desk nook at the bottom of the stairs. (There are nook's upstairs and downstairs!) The upstairs loft can be used for office space or a family entertainment area. Mstr bedroom opens with double doors and has a huge L shaped closet. This house is AMAZING!
